Class ConcurrentNavigableMapRateMeter

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Configurable<java.lang.Void>, RateMeter<java.lang.Void>

    @ThreadSafe
public final class ConcurrentNavigableMapRateMeter
extends AbstractNavigableMapRateMeter<ConcurrentRateMeterConfig>
    A thread-safe implementation of AbstractNavigableMapRateMeter, which uses ConcurrentSkipListMap implementation of NavigableMap (this might be changed in the future).
